Class ImageLayer

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.cmapi.primitives.GeoBase
      • mil.emp3.api.abstracts.MapService
        • mil.emp3.api.ImageLayer
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IImageLayer, IMapService, IGeoBase

    public class ImageLayer
extends MapService
implements IImageLayer
    This class implements an image map service layer. It imposes an image on the map at a specified location bounded by the provided bounding box.
